/* â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
   Historial persistente â€” logActivity + SafeStorage
   v1.0 Â· El manga como recurso didÃ¡ctico Â· ULPGC

   sessionLog: actividad de la sesiÃ³n actual (en memoria).
   SafeStorage: Ãºltimas 50/20 entradas por categorÃ­a (persistente).
   renderHistModal: muestra ambas secciones separadas.
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â• */

const HIST_KEY    = 'manga_hist_v1';
const HIST_LIMITS = { viewed: 50, searches: 20, ai: 20, compared: 20 };

/** Estado en memoria de la sesiÃ³n actual */
const sessionLog = { searches:[], viewed:[], compared:[], ai:[] };

/**
 * Registra una actividad en sessionLog Y en SafeStorage.
 * @param {'searches'|'viewed'|'compared'|'ai'} type
 * @param {Object} data
 */
function logActivity(type, data) {
  const now   = new Date();
  const time  = now.toLocaleTimeString('es-ES', { hour:'2-digit', minute:'2-digit' });
  const date  = now.toLocaleDateString('es-ES', { weekday:'short', day:'numeric', month:'short' });
  const entry = { ...data, time, date };

  sessionLog[type]?.push(entry);

  try {
    const stored = SafeStorage.getJSON(HIST_KEY, { searches:[], viewed:[], compared:[], ai:[] });
    const limit  = HIST_LIMITS[type] || 20;
    stored[type] = stored[type] || [];
    stored[type].unshift(entry);
    stored[type] = stored[type].slice(0, limit);
    SafeStorage.setJSON(HIST_KEY, stored);
  } catch { /* SafeStorage no disponible */ }
}

function openHist() { const _opener = document.activeElement; renderHistModal(); document.getElementById('histOverlay').classList.add('open'); document.body.style.overflow='hidden'; FocusTrap.activate(document.getElementById('histModal'), _opener); }
function closeHist() { document.getElementById('histOverlay').classList.remove('open'); document.body.style.overflow=''; FocusTrap.deactivate(); }

function renderHistModal() {
  const body = document.getElementById('histBody');
  if (!body) return;

  const sections = [
    { key:'viewed',   label:'TÃ­tulos consultados', render: e => `<strong>${escapeHtml(e.title||'')}</strong>${e.section ? ' Â· ' + escapeHtml(e.section) : ''}` },
    { key:'searches', label:'BÃºsquedas',           render: e => `<em>${escapeHtml(e.term||'')}</em>` },
    { key:'ai',       label:'Generaciones IA',     render: e => `${escapeHtml(e.type||'')}${e.titulo ? ': ' + escapeHtml(e.titulo) : ''}` },
    { key:'compared', label:'Comparativas',        render: e => (e.titles||[]).map(t => escapeHtml(t)).join(' vs ') },
  ];

  const totalActual = Object.values(sessionLog).reduce((s,a) => s + a.length, 0);
  let html = '';

  // â”€â”€ SesiÃ³n actual â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
  if (totalActual > 0) {
    html += '<div class="hist-group-header">SesiÃ³n actual</div>';
    html += sections.filter(s => sessionLog[s.key]?.length > 0).map(s =>
      `<div class="hist-section">
         <span class="hist-section-title">${escapeHtml(s.label)} (${sessionLog[s.key].length})</span>
         ${sessionLog[s.key].map(e =>
           `<div class="hist-item"><span class="hist-item-time">${escapeHtml(e.time||'')}</span>${s.render(e)}</div>`
         ).join('')}
       </div>`
    ).join('');
  } else {
    html += '<p class="hist-empty">AÃºn no hay actividad en esta sesiÃ³n.</p>';
  }

  // â”€â”€ Visitas anteriores â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€
  const stored = SafeStorage.getJSON(HIST_KEY, null);
  if (stored) {
    const currentKeys = new Set(Object.values(sessionLog).flat().map(e => e.date + e.time));
    const hasAnterior = sections.some(s => (stored[s.key]||[]).some(e => !currentKeys.has(e.date + e.time)));

    if (hasAnterior) {
      html += '<div class="hist-group-header hist-group-header--prev">Visitas anteriores</div>';
      html += sections.map(s => {
        const prev = (stored[s.key]||[]).filter(e => !currentKeys.has(e.date + e.time));
        if (!prev.length) return '';
        return `<div class="hist-section hist-section--prev">
          <span class="hist-section-title">${escapeHtml(s.label)} (${prev.length})</span>
          ${prev.map(e =>
            `<div class="hist-item"><span class="hist-item-date">${escapeHtml(e.date||'')} ${escapeHtml(e.time||'')}</span>${s.render(e)}</div>`
          ).join('')}
        </div>`;
      }).join('');
    }
  }

  body.innerHTML = html;
}

function exportHist() {
  const lines = [
    'HISTORIAL â€” Biblioteca Campus Obelisco ULPGC',
    new Date().toLocaleDateString('es-ES', { day:'2-digit', month:'long', year:'numeric' }),
    'â•'.repeat(50), ''
  ];
  const labels = { searches:'BÃšSQUEDAS', viewed:'TÃTULOS CONSULTADOS', compared:'COMPARATIVAS', ai:'GENERACIONES IA' };
  const stored  = SafeStorage.getJSON(HIST_KEY, {});
  const combined = {};
  ['searches','viewed','compared','ai'].forEach(key => {
    const current = sessionLog[key] || [];
    const prev    = (stored[key]||[]).filter(e => !current.some(c => c.date+c.time === e.date+e.time));
    combined[key] = [...current, ...prev];
  });
  for (const [key, items] of Object.entries(combined)) {
    if (!items.length) continue;
    lines.push(labels[key]); lines.push('â”€'.repeat(30));
    items.forEach(e => {
      const prefix = `  [${e.date ? e.date + ' ' : ''}${e.time}]`;
      if (key === 'searches')  lines.push(`${prefix} "${e.term}"`);
      if (key === 'viewed')    lines.push(`${prefix} ${e.title}${e.section ? ' (' + e.section + ')' : ''}`);
      if (key === 'compared')  lines.push(`${prefix} ${(e.titles||[]).join(' Â· ')}`);
      if (key === 'ai')        lines.push(`${prefix} ${e.type}${e.titulo ? ': ' + e.titulo : ''}`);
    });
    lines.push('');
  }
  _descargarBlob(new Blob([lines.join('\n')], { type:'text/plain;charset=utf-8' }), 'historial-manga.txt');
}

/** Limpia solo la sesiÃ³n actual */
function clearHist() { Object.keys(sessionLog).forEach(k => sessionLog[k] = []); closeHist(); }

/** Borra historial completo incluido SafeStorage */
function clearHistAll() {
  if (!confirm('Â¿Borrar el historial completo, incluidas las visitas anteriores guardadas en este navegador?')) return;
  Object.keys(sessionLog).forEach(k => sessionLog[k] = []);
  SafeStorage.removeItem(HIST_KEY);
  closeHist();
}
